{"word":"G2170 - εὐχάριστος - eucháristos - yoo-khar'-is-tos - Thankful","slug":"G2170","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐχάριστος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>eucháristos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yoo-khar'-is-tos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Thankful"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>εὐχάριστος</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>Eucharistos</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>yoo-khar'-is-tos</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> mindful of favours, grateful, thankful </p> <p class='li260'><b>2.</b> pleasing, agreeable </p> <p class='li260'><b>3.</b> acceptable to others, winning, liberal, beneficent </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: from <a href=\"#/G2095\">G2095</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G5483\">G5483</a> <p />- TDNT entry: 15:47,1 <p />- Part(s) of speech: Adjective <p />- Strong's: From <a href=\"#/G2095\">G2095</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G5483\">G5483</a>; <i>well favored</i> that is (by implication) <b><i>grateful</i></b>: - thankful. "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2168\">G2168</a>, <a href=\"#/G2169\">G2169</a>, <a href=\"#/G4796\">G4796</a>, <a href=\"#/G5463\">G5463</a>, <a href=\"#/G5479\">G5479</a>, <a href=\"#/G5483\">G5483</a>, <a href=\"#/G5484\">G5484</a>, <a href=\"#/G5485\">G5485</a>, <a href=\"#/G5486\">G5486</a>, <a href=\"#/G5487\">G5487</a>, <a href=\"#/G884\">G884</a>"}]}